biweekly.parameter

Class ParticipationStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • biweekly.parameter.EnumParameterValue
      • biweekly.parameter.VersionedEnumParameterValue
        • biweekly.parameter.ParticipationStatus

  • public class ParticipationStatus
extends VersionedEnumParameterValue
    Defines a calendar user's level of participation. Used with the Attendee property.
    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    RFC 5545 p.22-3, vCal 1.0 p.25-6

    • Field Detail

      • NEEDS_ACTION

        public static final ParticipationStatus NEEDS_ACTION
        Indicates that the user needs to make a decision about the item. Valid within the VEvent, VTodo, VJournal components.

      • ACCEPTED

        public static final ParticipationStatus ACCEPTED
        Indicates that the user has accepted the item. Valid within the VEvent, VTodo, VJournal components.

      • DECLINED

        public static final ParticipationStatus DECLINED
        Indicates that the user has declined the item. Valid within the VEvent, VTodo, VJournal components.

      • TENTATIVE

        public static final ParticipationStatus TENTATIVE
        Indicates that the user has tentatively accepted the item. Valid within the VEvent and VJournal components.

      • DELEGATED

        public static final ParticipationStatus DELEGATED
        Indicates that the user has delegated the item to someone else. Valid within the VEvent and VTodo components.

      • COMPLETED

        public static final ParticipationStatus COMPLETED
        Indicates that the user has completed the item. Only valid within the VTodo component.

      • IN_PROCESS

        public static final ParticipationStatus IN_PROCESS
        Indicates that the user is in the process of completing the item. Only valid within the VTodo component.

      • CONFIRMED

        public static final ParticipationStatus CONFIRMED
        Indicates that the user confirmed attendance. Only valid within the VEvent component of vCalendar version 1.0.

      • SENT

        public static final ParticipationStatus SENT
        Indicates that the item was sent out to the user. Valid within VEvent and VTodo components of vCalendar version 1.0.
